      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YANA'S GIRL (6) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Ballarat over 390m (22.38). Has placed a couple of times at this track. Won at her only start from this box. Can discover winning form. JUMBUK FUNI (1) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 5th and beaten 9 lengths at Geelong (23.45). Should be about the money. MABEL LEE ROSE (2) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 3.5 lengths (24.56) at Sale. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. FLEX FACTOR (3) has won at this course and distance, cannot be underestimated.",
